#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#                           REVISION HISTORY
#
#     Date        Author     Description
#     ----        ------     -----------
# 47. 2005-08-12  Stoeckley  Add flag CXX_IBSMA; change SO_LINK flags for
#                             all linux platforms to use g++ instead of ld.
