#                            flag.
# 42. 2005-05-02  Goodger    Removed NOFSEEKO -D flag from all platforms.
#                            Needed for large files.
# 41. 2005-05-02  Goodger    Add platform linuxab80_kruger.
# 40. 2005-04-28  Goodger    Add platform 64linuxp52.
# 39. 2005-04-25  Goodger    Add mvec to MATH_LIBS on 64sol62.
# 38. 2005-02-22  Goodger    Add platforms linuxg95 and linuxg95_debug.
